summary:
Motivated IT professional with 16+ years of experience, many of them as a software developer and 6+ leading both distributed and collocated agile teams of different sizes and technologies that provide value for clients worldwide in areas such as government, event management, financial and gaming, constantly adapting myself to new teams and clients.

Passionate about Agility, I have solid project management skills and software architecture abilities. I support the team by aligning the business requirements with strategy and also by guaranteeing constant process improvement.

My people-oriented personality and strong communication skills allow me to connect with the team and help generate a good working environment, where people are truly empowered and teams are self-managed.
